          "backward_split=32768 causes 2x slowdown due to memory pressure"
        ],
        "recommendation": "forward_split=1024 improves forward by ~4%, backward_split=16384 is already optimal. Neither meets the >5% threshold for automatic update. Consider vocab-size-dependent dynamic selection."
